    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Stoic and solid, a beasthide shifter draws strength and stability from the beast within. Beasthide shifters are typically tied to the bear or the boar, but any creature known for its toughness could apply.</p>\n<p><strong>Ability Score Increase.</strong> Your Constitution score increases by 2.</p>\n<p><strong>Tough.</strong> You have proficiency in the Athletics skill.</p>\n<p><strong>Shifting Feature.</strong> Whenever you shift, you gain [[/r 1d6]] additional temporary hit points, and while shifted, you have a +1 bonus to your AC.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: Edit the healing formula of your </em>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-racial-features.ZnC5wZ9QLAr54AXj]{Shifting}<em> feature to roll an additional 1d6.</em></p>\n</section>",
